com.google.web.bindery.autobean.gwt.client.impl
Class JsoSplittable

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      com.google.web.bindery.autobean.gwt.client.impl.JsoSplittable
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasSplittable, Splittable
@GwtScriptOnly
public final class JsoSplittable
extends JavaScriptObject
implements Splittable, HasSplittable

Implements the EntityCodex.Splittable interface using a raw JavaScriptObject.

A string value represented by a JsoSplittable can't use the string object directly, since String.prototype is overridden, so instead a temporary wrapper object is used to encapsulate the string data.
